    "navbar": "About Us\nFounder's Story\nVirtual Tour of Hammer HQ",
    "text": "1-800-336-1977 | Dealer Locator\nMY ACCOUNT\nFUELS\nSUPPLEMENTS\nCLOTHING & GEAR\nKNOWLEDGE\nENERGY · ENDURANCE · RECOVERY · SINCE 1987\nTOP FUELS\nRECOVERITE®\nHEED®\nHAMMER GEL®\nENDUROLYTES FIZZ®\nWHEY PROTEIN\nPERPETUEM®2.0\nVIEW ALL FUELS\nTOP SUPPLEMENTS\nTISSUE REJUVENATOR\nHAMMER CBD SOFTGELS\nPREMIUM INSURANCE CAPS\nRACE CAPS SUPREME\nMITO CAPS\nFULLY CHARGED\nVIEW ALL SUPPLEMENTS\nTOP KNOWLEDGE\nENDURANCE NEWS\n5 SECRETS OF SUCCESS\nHOW TO HAMMER\nCOOKBOOK\nVIEW ALL KNOWLEDGE\nGET STARTED\nDiscover Hammer Nutrition, the company and the product line.\nCATEGORIES TO EXPLORE\nRECOVERY\nENERGY\nHAMMER CBD\nDAILY ESSENTIALS\nFOOD BARS\nELECTROLYTES\nREAL REVIEWS FROM REAL CUSTOMERS\n0\n0\nStraight forward, clear, good pricing, excellent products. Enough said.\n11/30/2022\n0\nIt's always Hammer time\n11/29/2022\n0\nHammer products are great. the online catalog is organized and easy to find all products.\n11/28/2022\n0\nBrian Frank, Founder & CEO\nTHE HAMMER DIFFERENCE\nWe’re real people making real, natural, healthy products with tons of vital information and a singular desire to help you be your best!\nAbout Us\nFounder's Story\nVirtual Tour of Hammer HQ\nPRODUCTS\nOver 35 years of developing the most effective, natural products free of added sugars, artificial colors, flavors, chemicals and preservatives. We use only complex carbohydrates, the highest quality proteins and ingredients in our 100% USA made products.\nFuels   |   Recovery   |   Supplements\nKNOWLEDGE\nNo one knows more about properly fueling for any kind of exercise than Hammer! We literally wrote the book on it! Following our science based, real world proven, fueling techniques will eliminate all concerns of excessive fatigue, cramping, GI distress, or any other symptoms caused by poor fueling practices.\nEssential   |   Advanced   |   Endurance News\nSERVICE\nSecond to none, the best you've ever had! We treat you like you are important to us, because you are... Guaranteed!\nShipping   |   Privacy   |   Contact Us\n35 YEARS OF ENDURANCE\nSTAY AHEAD OF THE PACK\nSign up for our newsletter to get the latest in endurance news and performance tips.\nSUBSCRIBE\nHAMMER NUTRITION\nFounded in 1987 by Brian Frank, Hammer Nutrition provides superlative products, proprietary knowledge, and 5-star service to health conscious athletes all over the world.\nCOMPANY\nAbout Us\nOur Guarantee\nSponsorship\nCareers\nDealer Locator\nInternational\nRESOURCES\n2022 Catalog\n5 Secrets of Success\nHow to Hammer\nCookbook\nGift Cards\nClearance\nEDUCATION\nKnowledge Base\nEndurance News\nEndurance News Weekly\nFAQs\nSUPPORT\nShipping Policy\nPrivacy Policy\nFDA Disclaimer\nReturns & Exchanges\nContact Us\nCall 1-800-336-1977\n© Copyright 2022 Hammer Nutrition Direct",
